data.description: 1243 S Noyes is an adorable condo unit in one of Visalia's most desirable areas, Westgate. This quiet community features a sparkling pool and green parkway. You will immediately notice the vaulted ceilings in this spacious home. The main floor houses the living room, kitchen, dining, 1/2 bath and laundry room. Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The primary bedroom has 2 closets and french doors opening to a lovely balcony with a view of the pool and park area. The low maintenance backyard is perfect for grilling and entertaining and has newer artificial turf as well as posts ready to hang a shade sail or cafe lights. The oversized one car garage features additional space for storage. This unit has a carport and  room to park multiple vehicles. Don't miss your opportunity to view this cute home today.
